thumb.title: 【GUMi】Stand Tall【Synth V Cover】
thumb.description: SuperSoniker - Stand Tall (Megpoid Gumi Cover)Stream (Teto version): https://share.amuse.io/track/supersoniker-stand-tallLyrics: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1rsfbYnJbdZWWU7JW_Y_Wbw5lU_xOa-eHEyGK1Mh-rAk/Download: https://www.newgrounds.com/audio/download/1440083My social media: https://linktr.ee/supersonikerI made this Synthesizer V cover when I was experiencing problems distributing “Stand Tall” with Teto to platforms (which were solved anyway). During the days when I was working on this song, after finishing Teto's voice it occurred to me to also try Gumi's voice, now it is a cover that I loved, and its final result even gave me a lot of encouragement to share it, I hope you like this too.
